To Host the app and run it follqw the given steps:
1.Create folder and download the files given in the repositary like app.py,dataser file etc to folder.
2. Open the folder and VSCODE and open app.py file.
3.On terminal run the command: pip install streamlit pandas requests scikit-learn .This will install all dependencies.
4.To run on local host run command :streamlit run app.py.You will be directed to localHost and then choose the movie you wish for,You will get all the corresponding movies.

